Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:06.19,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,393)\fad(500,0)}December 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you--?! {\alpha&HFF&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you--?! Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L has died...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he killed by Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After saying he was going to sentence Kira to death, he got killed himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you're telling me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you win the game, {\alpha&HFF&}or solve the puzzle... you're nothing but a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you win the game, or solve the puzzle... {\alpha&HFF&}you're nothing but a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you win the game, or solve the puzzle... you're nothing but a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}who did L choose? Me or Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who did L choose? Me or Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:01:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hadn't decided yet... {\alpha&HFF&}and since he's dead, he can no longer choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hadn't decided yet... and since he's dead, he can no longer choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, {\alpha&HFF&}Near, how about it? Why don't you two try joining forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, Near, {\alpha&HFF&}how about it? Why don't you two try joining forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, Near, how about it? {\alpha&HFF&}Why don't you two try joining forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, Near, how about it? Why don't you two try joining forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, fine by me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that Near and I don't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've always been rivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who'll succeed L will be Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me, Near will handle things calmly and objectively, like he's solving a puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the orphanage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm almost 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to live my life my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time of Higuchi's arrest, a policeman overheard him say:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.57,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,394)\fad(500,0)}March 5th 2012
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you write the name of someone whose face you know in the notebook, that person will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's this "notebook of death"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}It should currently be in the possession of the Japanese police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It should currently be in the possession of the Japanese police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.42,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(336,82)\fad(750,450)}A boy who goes by the name of "Near",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:39.38,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(650,450)\pos(533,150)}armed with three years' worth \Nof independent research into \Nthe Kira investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:43.14,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(162,109)\fad(650,540)}approaches the President accompanied by the Head of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, the current L is a fake created by the Japanese police force in order to avoid disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real L is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Mason, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}let's just say he is L's true successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's just say he is L's true successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.08,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,78)\fad(650,450)}The United States of America...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:12.21,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad650,450)}SPK = Secret Provision for Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:12.21,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(177,145)\fad(650,450)}established the SPK, \Na brand-new counter-Kira organization \Nwith no links to L,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:18.71,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(168,110)\fad(650,450)}comprised of selected agents from the FBI and CIA, in addition to Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.76,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(364,362)}Abduction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}under the present circumstances, controlling information on the Internet is impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, under the present circumstances, controlling information on the Internet is impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the investigation into Kira has been at a standstill for far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who post the names of the people they want dead on the Internet are the ones I really want them to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because Kira requires information from the Internet, there's no way they'd kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely contradicting yourself, Matsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, certainly, the conclusion that as long as you don't do anything bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, that for law-abiding people in general, the world has changed for the better, {\alpha&HFF&}will be an easy conclusion for some people to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, that for law-abiding people in general, the world has changed for the better, will be an easy conclusion for some people to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fine one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, soon everyone will see it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all talking about that again? Give it a rest, darling. Same with you Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, Misa-san, it's a surprise to see you two here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse our intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Matsuda-san", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&HFF&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm indebted to you for always taking care of my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Sayu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sayu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you've really grown up... umm, you've become even more beautiful... erm, the last time I saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu's face has gone bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I didn't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let Sayu marry a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. There's no way I would allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:05:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! No way... I haven't even asked her out, let alone proposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fath--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I think Matsuda-san is lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really, Sayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and if you were maybe ten years younger, I might even have considered dating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've learned to handle yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she seems so much more mature than Matsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't changed at all. You've always been this wonderful from the moment I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you've got a job too now. Don't just live together, hurry up and get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a unfortunate family playing "happy families"... {\alpha&HFF&}this is too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a unfortunate family playing "happy families"... this is too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Aizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, Light. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abduction? {\alpha&HFF&}Who's abducted who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abduction? Who's abducted who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief of the Police Force, Takimura... {\alpha&HFF&}We have no idea who the culprit is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief of the Police Force, Takimura... We have no idea who the culprit is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why now, when the Kira investigation is in this state...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.45,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,0)\fnOffensiveBold\shad0\c&H484F4E&\3c&HB3BEB3&\pos(368,307)\frx340\t(0,3000,\fscx105\fscy105)}Deputy Chief's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received the call at 6:12pm; around 45 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've traced the call back to the Chief's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the culprit made any demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... {\alpha&HFF&}they'll exchange the Chief... for the murderer's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... they'll exchange the Chief... {\alpha&HFF&}for the murderer's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... they'll exchange the Chief... for the murderer's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing this and why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily. If people found out about the notebook there would be countless people who would want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, how much does the Chief know about the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information regarding the notebook was supposed to be kept to the people in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I swear I haven't told the Chief anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone knows about the existence of the Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}and that the police have it... and they're coming after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone knows about the existence of the Death Note, and that the police have it... {\alpha&HFF&}and they're coming after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone knows about the existence of the Death Note, and that the police have it... and they're coming after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notify all police departments of the abduction only.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the culprits made contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There's someone here to see Takimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm FBI agent John McEnroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my real name of course, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'm here regarding Kira, so please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my real name of course, but I'm here regarding Kira, so please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm afraid the Chief isn't available right now, but you can discuss the matter with me if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira... I'm afraid the Chief isn't available right now, but you can discuss the matter with me if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get straight to the point... {\alpha&HFF&}the Japanese police force can't be depended on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get straight to the point... the Japanese police force can't be depended on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to solve the Kira case, we'd like you to hand the notebook over to our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was the FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you hidden the Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act as if you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize this is a serious crime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing to gain by abducting the Chief of the Japanese police force!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how did you find out about the notebook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that someone has abducted the Chief of the police force, {\alpha&HFF&}and their aim seems to be to obtain the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that someone has abducted the Chief of the police force, and their aim seems to be to obtain the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Lester, {\alpha&HFF&}steer the conversation toward assisting them with the rescue of the Chief and apprehending the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Lester, steer the conversation toward assisting them with the rescue of the Chief and apprehending the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we get the chance, we'll seize the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the Japanese police backed out of the Kira investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in reality, the only ones working on the case with L were Yagami Souichirou, Mogi Kanzou and Matsuda Touta. {\alpha&HFF&}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in reality, the only ones working on the case with L were Yagami Souichirou, Mogi Kanzou and Matsuda Touta. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There was another man called Ukita, but he was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that explains why the Chief of the Police Force didn't even know of the notebook's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese police are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all them, the one with the highest rank was Yagami, the guy in command of headquarters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&HFF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my theory, there should be two notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has one, and the Japanese police has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we do as Mello says, nothing will go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the year and a half Mello's been here, has he been wrong about anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would someone like you, who joined us by bringing the head of a mafia boss that even Kira hadn't managed to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be so hung up over a notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't just want the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill anyone who gets in my way, {\alpha&HFF&}and become number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill anyone who gets in my way, and become number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes to beat Near to it.
Comment: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry... Eddie and I were kinda dozing off and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takimura has managed to kill himself using his necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! This won't work without a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is Kira's work, it means they don't know our names or faces, so they killed Takimura instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira is someone who knows about this abduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, Kira is someone who knows about this abduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, we'll abduct Yagami Souichirou's daughter, Yagami Sayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no clues regarding the whereabouts of the Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits haven't made further contact since abducting him. What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light. {\alpha&HFF&}That FBI agent called himself "John McEnroe"... His real name is Rally Connors, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light. That FBI agent called himself "John McEnroe"... {\alpha&HFF&}His real name is Rally Connors, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light. That FBI agent called himself "John McEnroe"... His real name is Rally Connors, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? {\alpha&HFF&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation is real too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Head of the FBI himself offered his assistance in rescuing the Chief... {\alpha&HFF&}I guess we can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Head of the FBI himself offered his assistance in rescuing the Chief... I guess we can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief should already be dead... {\alpha&HFF&}why haven't they said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief should already be dead... why haven't they said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead, so they're just giving up the exchange? {\alpha&HFF&}Is that the kind of opponent they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead, so they're just giving up the exchange? Is that the kind of opponent they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... {\alpha&HFF&}no, everyone else that's here too. You all need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... no, everyone else that's here too. You all need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Chief doesn't know about the notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}he knows who was investigating alongside L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Chief doesn't know about the notebook, he knows who was investigating alongside L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he reveals that, there is a chance that they'll come after us--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to bed by myself tonight, like a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people here aren't the only ones in danger! {\alpha&HFF&}Our families and--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people here aren't the only ones in danger! Our families and--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief's cell phone number... {\alpha&HFF&}it's from the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief's cell phone number... it's from the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trace the call!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief... {\alpha&HFF&}about the deal regarding the exchange of the Chief for the notebook... that's now off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief... about the deal regarding the exchange of the Chief for the notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}that's now off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief... about the deal regarding the exchange of the Chief for the notebook... that's now off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takimura is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Y-{\alpha&HFF&}You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal is only off as far as the Chief is concerned. {\alpha&HFF&}Instead, we'll now exchange the notebook in return for Yagami Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal is only off as far as the Chief is concerned. Instead, we'll now exchange the notebook in return for Yagami Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Deputy Chief of the Police, we know it's pointless to tell you not to contact the police, but we would like you to act alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we see any big movements by the police, we'll kill your daughter, without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we did with the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sending you images of Takimura's corpse. Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-{\alpha&HFF&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got me! {\alpha&HFF&}They've manipulated Takimura's death to their own advantage, and now Sayu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got me! They've manipulated Takimura's death to their own advantage, and now Sayu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, things are getting interesting again, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they have to go this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:50.16,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\c&H56514B&\3c&H2E2421&\fnOffensiveBold\frz0.381\move(402,177,373,177,0,3320)}YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling? Isn't this rather unusual of you? Calling from your work cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, she's pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I figure it, the kidnappers didn't kill the Chief; Kira did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably did that to prevent the kidnappers from acquiring the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira prefers to think of themselves as just, so they wouldn't want the notebook falling into evil hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira did kill the Chief, then we've got to assume that they have some way of accessing police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're better off if we act by using only the people here. {\alpha&HFF&}If we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're better off if we act by using only the people here. If we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira may try and kill the hostage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}the abducted Chief of the Japanese police has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, the abducted Chief of the Japanese police has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By whom? {\alpha&HFF&}By the people that abducted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By whom? By the people that abducted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be interesting if it turns out that Kira was the one who killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. If the hostage dies, then they'd be unable to exchange him for the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}it narrows the list of suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it was Kira, it narrows the list of suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Commander Lester, {\alpha&HFF&}any news on his whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Commander Lester, any news on his whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}it's certain that four years ago he was at the orphanage you mentioned... after that, we have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's certain that four years ago he was at the orphanage you mentioned... {\alpha&HFF&}after that, we have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's certain that four years ago he was at the orphanage you mentioned... after that, we have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, you always get too emotional and neglect what's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you really have nothing to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange that you'd leave a photo of yourself behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter has finally arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have an idea as to where we are by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do the exchange here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone. {\alpha&HFF&}With the notebook. Within two days. In LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone. With the notebook. {\alpha&HFF&}Within two days. In LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone. With the notebook. Within two days. {\alpha&HFF&}In LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone. With the notebook. Within two days. In LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no exchange unless you guarantee that my daughter is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it. I'll mail you a picture of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief! We've narrowed it down to Los Angeles' Fifth Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The TV program pictured in the background is currently airing in the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken it on purpose to let us know she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}Thank god... at least we know she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank god... {\alpha&HFF&}at least we know she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank god... at least we know she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the notebook to LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going as the Deputy Chief of the Police Force, and also as Yagami Sayu's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make all the decisions and accept full responsibility for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Wait until we've worked out a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Deputy Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got to get to LA within two days. There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that the kidnappers didn't kill Takimura; Kira did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just mentioning it as a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, Kira somehow managed to obtain information from the Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's L... {\alpha&HFF&}the current one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's L... the current one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard what John McEnroe, {\alpha&HFF&}or Agent Rally Connors, had to say from Deputy Chief Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard what John McEnroe, or Agent Rally Connors, {\alpha&HFF&}had to say from Deputy Chief Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard what John McEnroe, or Agent Rally Connors, had to say from Deputy Chief Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you assist us in the investigation into the murder of Chief Takimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second-generation L... {\alpha&HFF&}it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second-generation L... it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Second-generation"? {\alpha&HFF&}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Second-generation"? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a newly established organization especially created to investigate Kira independently of L, called the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seven main members of this organization all know about L's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's death? {\alpha&HFF&}Who and where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's death? Who and where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am the one at the center of the SPK...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm N.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... I'm N.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"N"? {\alpha&HFF&}Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"N"? Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... {\alpha&HFF&}this feeling... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... this feeling... {\alpha&HFF&}what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... this feeling... what is it?
